sub_title: Process Automation Engineer at Ekro / VanDrie Group
summary:
Team-focused mechanical engineer with a passion for automobiles and manufacturing. Major experience
in automation of production/assembly processes with a focus on collaborative robots. Project history
includes the analysis and optimization of manufacturing systems to maximize efficiency.
